high_descs: Turn left, go past the table to the sink.
Take the knife from the sink.
Cut the tomato in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right to face the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn around, go in front of the green bin to the left of the oven.
Put the slice of tomato in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a bin.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the sink
Pick up the knife from the sink
Slice the tomato in the sink with your knife
Put the knife back in the sink
Pick up the sliced tomato in the sink
Turn to your right and face the microwave
Place the tomato inside the microwave and cook it. Take it out when it's done
Turn around and face the trash bin to the left of the oven
Put the tomato inside the trash bin
Go to the sink to your left.
Pick up the knife from in the sink
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink to the right of the tomato.
Take a tomato slice from the sink.
Go to the microwave to your right.
Cook the tomato in the microwave.
Take the tomato slice to the trash bin behind you.
Put the cooked tomato slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato slice in the trash bin.
